Source.Name: languagetool
Source.Summary: Style and Grammar Checker for 25+ Languages
Source.Description: LanguageTool is an Open Source proofreading software for English, French, German, Polish, Russian, and more than 20 other languages. It finds many errors that a simple spell checker cannot detect.
